originalText.text: She changed my life. I can't imagine my life without her. She is one of the greatest gifts I have received in my life. She was the only one who believed in me for several years. No one doubts that she's a smart psychologist, but she's a very patient and good person. I really appreciate her.

originalText.text:
Hi! I had my first visit with Doctor Nimroody. At first, she seemed nice and very approachable, and easy to talk to, but as the hour went by she didn’t seem to follow nor listen to my concerns. At that point I didn’t even want to continue the session but I did. When she started talking I smelled alcohol on her breath and I said to myself, this is real strange, I should just finish this up and never come back.
She was referred to me by a friend of mine, as I had just moved to the area, I took her recommendation. But I will never ever be back to this office to see this Doctor.
Hope this helps.
